dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Toledo, sheet 51. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 40.0000. South Decimal Degree 39.0000. East Decimal Degree -4.0000. West Decimal Degree -5.0000. Alternate title: Toledo, Spain. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, 1882, 1938; Spain, 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisimo, 1931-1939; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:400,000, A.M.S., Sheets 46 and 47, Third Edition, 1943; Railways of Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, G.S.G.S., 1942, corrected from Intelligence Reports, 1941-1943. Partially revised from aerial photography, 1943.".
